Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.77,0:02:14.69,Episode Title,SCREEN,0000,0000,0000,,“And the town still turns {\c&H0604E8&}(part A){\c&HFFFFFF&}” from Vol. 2 {\c&H338803&}Ch. 13{\c&HFFFFFF&}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:11.27,0:02:14.49,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, so this is the café you work at?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:14.49,0:02:16.94,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't you be at ping pong practice right now?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:17.16,0:02:19.11,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,I'm ditching today. Can I order now?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:19.35,0:02:20.32,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, what’cha want?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:20.57,0:02:22.79,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,Cutlet curry, hold the cutlets.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:22.79,0:02:25.04,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,And an iced coffee, hold the ice. And make it hot.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:25.04,0:02:26.00,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Come again?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:26.00,0:02:27.91,Default,Tat,0000,0000,0000,,So you just want curry and coffee, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:28.67,0:02:30.50,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't talking to you, dumbass.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:30.50,0:02:34.63,Default,Tat,0000,0000,0000,,So very sorry. I just work here too, that's all.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:34.63,0:02:37.84,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's going on here? It's kinda tense in here.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:39.01,0:02:41.24,Default,Tat,0000,0000,0000,,She was an upperclassman at my middle school.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:41.24,0:02:44.14,Default,Tat,0000,0000,0000,,She's all pissy because I didn't join the ping-pong club in high school.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:45.26,0:02:48.78,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,She gave up 'cause she couldn't beat me, so she ran away, the little wuss.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:48.78,0:02:50.90,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,I won't take you back now, even if you beg me to.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:50.90,0:02:53.98,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, quit fighting over such a stupid disagreement.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:53.98,0:02:57.49,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah! I've got just the thing for you two.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:58.28,0:03:01.28,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,The magnifying pendant! {see next few lines}
Dialogue: 5,0:03:04.20,0:03:06.16,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,At first glance, it looks like an ordinary magnifying glass.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:06.16,0:03:09.21,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,But wait! The other end is actually a fountain pendant!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:09.21,0:03:11.87,Default,Uki,0000,0000,0000,,That's fountain PEN. No "dant".
Dialogue: 5,0:03:11.87,0:03:14.00,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,It's a little heavy, but it still writes great.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.87,0:03:14.00,Sign,WRITING,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs80\bord0\c&H3A454F&\b0\frz12.327\fnBurst My Bubble\pos(551,240)}Kon is a doofus
Dialogue: 5,0:03:14.00,0:03:18.43,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Two completely different instruments, combined into one amazing detective tool!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:18.43,0:03:20.97,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,So you two stop fighting and get along with each other!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:21.22,0:03:26.42,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I thought I could work this out just like Moori Motonari's "3 arrows" story.{TL note would be appropriate, but whatever.}
Dialogue: 5,0:03:26.42,0:03:28.22,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,But it seems like they're not getting it.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:28.42,0:03:31.39,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,This pen looks like it was a gift.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:31.39,0:03:34.95,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Well yeah. How many high school girls can afford a foutain pendant?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:34.95,0:03:36.98,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,My uncle gave it to me as a present when I entered high school.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:38.42,0:03:40.07,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,This is a Montblanc. {a brand of pen? idk much about pens}{It has a fancy french name so w/e}
Dialogue: 5,0:03:40.30,0:03:43.41,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm sorry, but we don't serve montblancs here.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:43.41,0:03:44.47,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,We've got coffee jelly, though.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:44.47,0:03:47.58,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,No, not the food. Did you modify this yourself?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:47.58,0:03:50.30,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Sure did! I'm gonna patent this!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:50.30,0:03:54.50,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,I just chopped off the end of the pen, and super glued the magnifying glass to it!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:54.50,0:03:57.40,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,Well, as long as you knew what you were doing, I guess it's okay.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:57.40,0:03:59.76,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,But Monblanc pens are pretty fancy, you know.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:00.01,0:04:03.44,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,I think they cost tens of thousands of yen. {couple hundred $}{we’ve used yen throughout the entire series, so for consistency’s sake...}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:05.01,0:04:07.81,Default,Uki,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to burst your bubble Hotori,
Dialogue: 5,0:04:07.81,0:04:10.81,Default,Uki,0000,0000,0000,,but someone's beat you to the punch.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:10.81,0:04:15.04,Default,Uki,0000,0000,0000,,See? The pen cap has a magnifying glass on it.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:15.04,0:04:17.15,Default,Uki,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty popular among us old folk.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:18.65,0:04:22.19,Default,Uki,0000,0000,0000,,You can go home early today. Get some rest.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:22.19,0:04:24.11,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... I think I've got something you might like.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:24.76,0:04:25.62,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,Found it!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:25.88,0:04:28.62,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,Here. You can have this whistle, so cheer up, okay?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:29.62,0:04:31.44,Default,Tat,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you going to change out of that?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:32.35,0:04:34.76,Default,Tat,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't your house the other way?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:35.75,0:04:39.54,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,So that's the look of someone who's lost everything they used to believe in.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:39.54,0:04:41.99,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,It's like she's been dowsed in despair.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:41.99,0:04:45.47,Default,Tat,0000,0000,0000,,Desperately seeking a light of hope amidst the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.51,0:04:50.10,Sign,SCREEN,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\an7\pos(691,253)\c&H183B61&}Incoming call\NAyatori Residence
Dialogue: 5,0:04:52.23,0:04:54.35,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Arashiyama residence...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:54.35,0:04:55.60,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Uncle!?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:55.80,0:04:58.44,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,What impeccable timing you have.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:58.70,0:05:01.53,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,That? Oh, you meant the fountain pendant?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:01.53,0:05:03.47,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, of course I'm using it!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:03.47,0:05:06.75,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,I always carry it with me. I've got it with me right here.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:06.75,0:05:10.12,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, how much did this cost, exactly?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:10.12,0:05:10.97,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,A hundred thou- {~1100$}{the pen better be made of gold}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:11.27,0:05:15.96,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,During summer vacation? Yes, I'd love to come visit.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:16.18,0:05:17.46,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:17.98,0:05:20.71,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Hey mom, phone call from the Ayatoris.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:20.71,0:05:23.21,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, thanks. Hey, what about work?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.21,0:05:25.67,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\fnCorporate Rounded\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(802,99)}Come visit us\N over summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.21,0:05:25.67,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\fnCorporate Rounded\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(283,535)}I'll refill the ink for you.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:28.11,0:05:30.35,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,It's the de-cap-itation caper!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:31.47,0:05:33.61,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, think positive.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:33.61,0:05:38.19,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just come up with some kind of trick to distract him when I visit.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:38.19,0:05:41.45,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,A trick... mysteries have tricks...
Dialogue: 5,0:05:41.45,0:05:45.61,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Mysteries... I wonder when Hiroto Shimabe's new book is coming out.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:45.61,0:05:49.12,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Mystery Magazine published any updates on it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.11,0:05:50.24,Sign,MAGAZINE,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\bord0\c&H57A2D1&\fnZETSUBOUSHITA\pos(672,274)}Mystery Magazine
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.11,0:05:50.24,Sign,MAGAZINE,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\bord0\fnZETSUBOUSHITA\c&H180C80&\pos(642,168)}Weekly
Dialogue: 5,0:05:50.24,0:05:51.95,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:53.12,0:05:55.79,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.83,0:05:58.62,Sign,MAGAZINE top right square,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&H434B5D&\frz1.275\pos(811,201)}Grand \N Prize
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.83,0:05:58.62,Sign,MAGAZINE top right square,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&H434B5D&\frz0.937\pos(709,436)}5 million yen for typed entries
Dialogue: 5,0:05:55.79,0:05:57.88,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,First prize, 5 million yen!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:57.88,0:05:58.92,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,That's more than enough!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:58.92,0:06:01.09,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,The deadline's coming up soon.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:01.09,0:06:03.10,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,But they'll publish 3 months from now.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:03.10,0:06:04.37,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,I can still make it!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:04.37,0:06:07.17,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,I can buy another fountain pendant by summer!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:07.84,0:06:14.56,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,No, writing a detective story and getting the prize money is the ONLY way to get another fountain pendant!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:14.56,0:06:17.27,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,What would I do if I actually won first prize, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.27,0:06:18.73,Sign,DOOR,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\fs55\bord0\fnBirdie\pos(658,233)\c&H181917&}Do not disturb
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.27,0:06:18.73,Sign,DOOR,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\fs35\bord0\fnBirdie\pos(648,462)\c&H181917&}Snacks and refreshments are appreciated
Dialogue: 5,0:06:19.30,0:06:24.40,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,I stood on the deck of the ship, watching the waves and enjoying my jell-o. {can we say jell-o?}{changed it}
Dialogue: 5,0:06:24.99,0:06:29.66,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,But little did I know that a horrifying incident was about to take place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.65,0:06:32.16,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs80\bord0\fnEPSON Pwwww\c&H000000&\pos(640,536)}Mur{\c&H4438B4&}der {\c&H000000&}on Jelly Island
Dialogue: 5,0:06:33.91,0:06:35.89,Default,San,0000,0000,0000,,I can see Jelly Island!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:35.89,0:06:38.44,Default,Har,0000,0000,0000,,So that's Jelly Island, home of the world-famous jelly...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:38.44,0:06:41.54,Default,Tat,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard stories of an Abominable Jellyman that lives on the island.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:41.54,0:06:43.34,Default,Tat,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so scared!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:45.24,0:06:50.05,Default,Uki,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome, friends. I am the master of Jelly Island.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:50.25,0:06:52.49,Default,Uki,0000,0000,0000,,Please, help yourselves to some jelly.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:52.49,0:06:54.54,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,I want strawberry jelly.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:54.54,0:06:56.47,Default,Tat,0000,0000,0000,,This person might be the Jellyman!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:56.69,0:06:58.34,Default,San,0000,0000,0000,,This is some pretty good jelly, huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:58.34,0:07:00.94,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Verily. Jelly Island's jelly is quite delectable.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:03.23,0:07:04.44,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,What happened!?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:05.73,0:07:08.33,Default,Har,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! Tatsuno's dead!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:08.33,0:07:10.03,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,She's been decapitated!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:10.03,0:07:11.36,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Who could have done such a thing?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:11.36,0:07:13.99,Default,Har,0000,0000,0000,,The legend of the Abominable Jellyman was true!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:13.99,0:07:16.33,Default,Asai,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody stay together!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:16.33,0:07:18.66,Default,San,0000,0000,0000,,The murderer might be one of us!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:18.66,0:07:20.41,Default,Har,0000,0000,0000,,No, the Jellyman did it! {is this supposed to be a question acf? changed from “?” to “!”}
Dialogue: 5,0:07:20.62,0:07:23.79,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,I don't trust any of you! I'm going on alone!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:27.30,0:07:29.17,Default,Har,0000,0000,0000,,That was Kon's scream!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:30.55,0:07:32.55,Default,Har,0000,0000,0000,,Now Kon's been killed too!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:34.43,0:07:36.94,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Heh, now I know who the culprit is.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:36.94,0:07:43.11,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was strange that the body of the first victim, Tatsuno, disappeared without a trace.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:43.11,0:07:45.23,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,But in fact, it's just the opposite!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:46.36,0:07:48.11,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,The murderer is YOU!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:48.11,0:07:49.44,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Kon!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:49.44,0:07:51.19,Default,Asai,0000,0000,0000,,But she's already dead!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:52.01,0:07:54.95,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't blood. It's strawberry jelly.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:55.15,0:07:58.45,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Observe. She merely buried herself!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:58.45,0:08:01.46,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,The only victim here is Tatsuno!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:01.69,0:08:06.50,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! She wouldn't join the ping pong club, so I killed her!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:06.72,0:08:09.07,Default,Tea,0000,0000,0000,,All right, you're going downtown.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:09.07,0:08:12.16,Default,Tea,0000,0000,0000,,Splendid work as always, Ms. Arashiyama.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:12.16,0:08:14.18,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector Moriaki. {<3}{Commented your heart out acf. You can’t have that in subs lol...}
Dialogue: 5,0:08:14.18,0:08:16.34,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,'Twas a dreadful case...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:16.34,0:08:22.27,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,But perhaps Kon was also a victim... of society.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:22.27,0:08:23.52,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,The end. {end of story, no more quotes if applicable}
Dialogue: 5,0:08:30.13,0:08:32.16,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,You sure seem happy today.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:32.16,0:08:34.91,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,You looked like you hadn't been getting enough sleep recently.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:37.38,0:08:39.14,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Kon...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:39.14,0:08:41.69,Default,Tat,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Arashiyama, when is your next book coming out?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:41.69,0:08:43.61,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,Please give me your autograph!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:43.61,0:08:45.55,Default,Tea,0000,0000,0000,,Me too, if you don't mind, Ms. Arashiyama!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:45.55,0:08:48.49,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone line up and prepare more flattery for me.{lol, I love this line}
Dialogue: 5,0:08:48.49,0:08:51.01,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll still come visit you when I'm famous.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:51.20,0:08:52.13,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.51,0:08:53.72,Sign,SCREEN,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\b1\fs60\fnCorporate Rounded\pos(640,469)\c&HF0EEEC&}However, one week later...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:53.92,0:08:55.34,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:56.31,0:08:57.14,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? I got something from Mystery Magazine.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:57.38,0:09:02.30,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,It's still a long time before they announce the winners...
Dialogue: 5,0:09:02.68,0:09:08.19,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see..."Thank you very much for your entry.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:08.19,0:09:16.45,Default,Ara/TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,However, we regret to inform you that your submission did not advance past the initial round of our rigorous evaluation."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.04,0:09:25.04,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\b1\fs100\fnCorporate Rounded\pos(640,520)\c&H070806&}Rigorous
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.04,0:09:27.04,Default,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\b1\fs100\fnCorporate Rounded\pos(640,520)\c&H070806&}Submission{don’t have the video, but shouldn’t this be “Evaluation”?}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.04,0:09:29.04,Default,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\b1\fs100\fnCorporate Rounded\pos(640,520)\c&H070806&}Initial Round
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.04,0:09:31.09,Default,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\bord0\b1\fs58\fnCorporate Rounded\c&H070806&\pos(202,535)}Please do not be discouraged. Rather, we look forward to seeing you improve as a writer.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:34.86,0:09:38.03,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,T-This can't be happening!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:38.03,0:09:41.26,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,I spent two whole weeks writing that! It's not fair!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:49.19,0:09:51.89,Default,Driver,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey little girl, you okay!?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:51.89,0:09:53.40,Default,Dri,0000,0000,0000,,Call an ambulance!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:55.05,0:09:58.32,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for jumping out in front of you like that.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:58.32,0:09:59.83,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine though, don't worry.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:59.83,0:10:01.07,Default,Dri,0000,0000,0000,,I'm calling an ambulance righ now, okay?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:01.07,0:10:03.06,Default,Dri2,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Don't move the body!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:03.65,0:10:04.91,Default,Dri,0000,0000,0000,,Oh man, she's a goner...
Dialogue: 5,0:10:05.54,0:10:10.29,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, this might be a little... no, a BIG problem.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:10.93,0:10:12.55,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I can see through myself!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:12.78,0:10:15.30,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! I'm floating!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:15.30,0:10:16.63,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what gives!?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:16.85,0:10:19.05,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't funny!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:26.31,0:10:28.44,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, something's coming!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:28.44,0:10:30.04,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Who the heck are you guys!?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:30.04,0:10:31.06,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Go away! Shoo!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:32.20,0:10:34.12,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,No really, this isn't a good time.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:34.12,0:10:36.65,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,I said wait! Put me back down!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:36.65,0:10:39.53,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, if you're just gonna goof off, can you let me slide this time?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:40.80,0:10:45.39,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Is that supposed to be my life flashing before my eyes!?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:47.50,0:10:50.41,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The city is home to many people.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:50.41,0:10:54.75,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,And just like that, there is now one less.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:58.67,0:11:01.30,Default,God,0000,0000,0000,,Place thine heart upon this scale.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.67,0:11:06.60,Episode Title,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,“And the town still turns {\c&HF38106&}(part B){\c&HFFFFFF&}” from Vol. 2 {\c&H03EDED&}Ch. 14
Dialogue: 5,0:11:01.50,0:11:04.50,Default,God,0000,0000,0000,,If thine heart is of lesser weight than this plum, thou may enter heaven.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:04.50,0:11:05.68,Default,God,0000,0000,0000,,Be it heavier, and thou be banished to hell.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:06.85,0:11:09.35,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way a heart could be lighter than a feather!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:10.69,0:11:12.71,Default,God,0000,0000,0000,,No! The holy feather!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:12.71,0:11:15.05,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Think of something better to compare it to.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:15.05,0:11:16.57,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Like a can of coffee or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.32,0:11:18.19,Sign,ARMBAND,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\an8\pos(640,40)}Annoying Moving Armband That I Don't Want To Typeset: Guide
Dialogue: 5,0:11:18.19,0:11:20.13,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here!?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:20.13,0:11:23.00,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,You're Japanese, so get in the Japanese line!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:23.74,0:11:28.20,Default,God,0000,0000,0000,,Come back here you little brat! I’ll throw you into hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.20,0:11:34.58,Sign,SIGN (MIDDLE),0000,0000,0000,,{\fscy80\bord0\c&H5D6A70&\pos(542,73)}Deceased Reception Desk
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.20,0:11:34.58,Sign,SIGN (MIDDLE),0000,0000,0000,,{\fs23\bord0\pos(547,158)\c&H829298&}Please wait quietly until your name is called.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:30.21,0:11:34.59,Default,Clerk,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Arashiyama... Ms. Hotori Arashiyama...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:35.79,0:11:38.42,Default,Worker,0000,0000,0000,,Okay... Ms. Hotori Arashiyama, yes?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:38.42,0:11:40.14,Default,Wor,0000,0000,0000,,Is this you first time dying?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:40.14,0:11:41.18,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:41.18,0:11:44.02,Default,Wor,0000,0000,0000,,Cause of death: accident. No negative karma.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:44.02,0:11:45.05,Default,Wor,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, that will be all.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:45.62,0:11:50.43,Default,Wor,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't any problems, so you should receive your proof of residence in about 2 to 3 weeks.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:55.44,0:11:58.07,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,This place kinda reminds me of city hall.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:58.29,0:12:00.32,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Hi there, sorry about before.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:00.32,0:12:04.07,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,My job is to assist new residents, so feel free to ask me anything.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:07.84,0:12:09.75,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Is this really the afterlife?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:09.75,0:12:11.79,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,It's not exactly how I pictured it.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:11.79,0:12:14.63,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody's got halos or those triangle thingies?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:14.84,0:12:19.29,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,We stopped doing those decades ago to cut costs.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:20.13,0:12:23.13,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,It's not quite the same, but you can have this.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:24.47,0:12:25.70,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, pretty.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:25.70,0:12:28.35,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,It looks great on you. It's called a "silent flower".
Dialogue: 5,0:12:28.59,0:12:31.95,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause dead men tell no tales! Get it?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:32.74,0:12:34.14,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,I've always wanted to say that.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:34.14,0:12:36.65,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Wasn't that hilarious?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:37.90,0:12:39.72,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to kill me?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:39.72,0:12:42.40,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Lay off, would you? I just died y'know!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:42.40,0:12:43.90,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,How about a little consideration?
