Dialogue: 5,0:12:50.16,0:12:53.29,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,The one and only place in Heaven where you can interact with the world of the living.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:53.29,0:12:55.47,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,How about we have some fun?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:55.47,0:12:57.40,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,It's on me today.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:57.40,0:12:59.80,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,So they've got photo booths in heaven too?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:01.38,0:13:04.81,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Photo booth? Honestly, you living folk...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:04.81,0:13:07.80,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Don't treat me like I'm some hick visiting the city. {more like Jed Clampett, amirite}{lol}
Dialogue: 5,0:13:09.72,0:13:12.49,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,This is called "Spirit Photoshop".
Dialogue: 5,0:13:12.49,0:13:15.15,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,You can make ordinary Earth pictures into spirit shots.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:15.15,0:13:16.42,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds like fun!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:16.42,0:13:19.17,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,If you have anyone in mind, go right ahead.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:19.48,0:13:20.36,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,How about Kon?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:20.57,0:13:21.97,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,What's her full name?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:21.97,0:13:22.86,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Futaba Kon.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:22.86,0:13:26.66,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect! It just so happens she recently dropped some off to be developed.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:27.17,0:13:31.24,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Now we buy hands, faces or poses, {lit: subject matter}and place them in any photo you like.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:31.44,0:13:33.86,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, does it have bunny ears?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:33.86,0:13:36.33,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't bunny ears make for a hilarious picture?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:37.83,0:13:41.88,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, those kinds of poses are rather expensive.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:41.88,0:13:45.46,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,It's a bit pricey for us common folk.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:45.46,0:13:46.62,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:46.62,0:13:49.52,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff like faces, fists, or will-o’-the-wisps are much cheaper.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:49.52,0:13:52.60,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder all those pictures look the same.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:52.84,0:13:55.53,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll go with this hand then.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:58.27,0:14:03.09,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I've tweaked her picture, I wanna see Kon's reaction.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:03.09,0:14:05.36,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:05.60,0:14:08.36,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Okay then, you can try these next.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:08.36,0:14:11.41,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Deposit 100 yen, and you can view the Earth for a brief time.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:12.87,0:14:14.37,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I see it!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:15.07,0:14:16.25,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,It's a bath house.
