Dialogue: 5,0:14:19.71,0:14:22.29,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Mosaics?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:22.29,0:14:24.95,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Private places cannot be viewed.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:24.95,0:14:28.43,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah... whatever happened to my body anyway?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:28.63,0:14:29.63,Default,BUILDING,0000,0000,0000,,Maruko Hospital
Dialogue: 5,0:14:29.83,0:14:31.53,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, there's mom.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:32.15,0:14:36.45,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,So you're saying Hotori's going to be like that permanently?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:36.45,0:14:41.31,Default,Doc,0000,0000,0000,,It breaks my heart to say this, but we don't believe she'll ever regain consciousness.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:41.31,0:14:42.82,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be...
Dialogue: 5,0:14:42.82,0:14:46.11,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Please, you've got to do something! Please doctor!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:44.60,0:14:47.24,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Where's dad running off to?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:48.45,0:14:50.07,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Takeru... Yukiko...
Dialogue: 5,0:14:50.07,0:14:51.80,Default,Tak,0000,0000,0000,,Stop crying, Yukiko.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:51.80,0:14:53.35,Default,Tak,0000,0000,0000,,I said stop crying!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:54.96,0:14:57.41,Default,Tak,0000,0000,0000,,Crying's not gonna bring her back.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:00.37,0:15:03.92,Default,Tak,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I said stop... crying!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:11.67,0:15:14.88,Default,Har,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why did this have to happen?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:14.88,0:15:17.85,Default,Har,0000,0000,0000,,What did Arashiyama do to deserve this?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:18.33,0:15:22.31,Default,Tat,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be okay. Hotori will get better.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:23.02,0:15:25.15,Default,Har,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know that for sure?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:25.15,0:15:26.28,Default,Tat,0000,0000,0000,,I just do!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:26.28,0:15:28.68,Default,Har,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give me that crap!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:28.68,0:15:30.20,Default,Har,0000,0000,0000,,How can you say that so easily!?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:30.20,0:15:31.16,Default,Tat,0000,0000,0000,,Because!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:31.80,0:15:33.99,Default,Tat,0000,0000,0000,,Becuase Hotori can't die yet! She just can't!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:42.10,0:15:44.53,Default,Tea,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... I see...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:44.53,0:15:46.32,Default,Tea,0000,0000,0000,,You have my condolences.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:46.32,0:15:48.26,Default,Tea,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. Please excuse me.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:02.06,0:16:05.39,Default,Bald,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care! Bring me that fucking driver's head right now!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:05.69,0:16:08.00,Default,Bald,0000,0000,0000,,I'll run HIM over with my truck!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:08.00,0:16:09.74,Default,Cop,0000,0000,0000,,Just calm down, guys!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:09.74,0:16:12.99,Default,Bald,0000,0000,0000,,Huh!? You trying to defend him?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:12.99,0:16:15.70,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna regret it, pal!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:16.90,0:16:18.36,Default,Fat,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, guys.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:18.36,0:16:21.83,Default,Fat,0000,0000,0000,,Hotori would resent us for that.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:23.33,0:16:27.34,Default,Cop,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. My business here is finished.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:35.43,0:16:40.93,Default,Uki,0000,0000,0000,,Zenji, please watch over Hotori for me. Please...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:42.70,0:16:47.40,Default,Gra,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Uki... there's nothing I can do.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:49.84,0:16:53.57,Default,San,0000,0000,0000,,WHY!? Why did you have to die, Arashiyama!?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:53.77,0:16:57.74,Default,San,0000,0000,0000,,I... I never got to tell you how I feel...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:58.00,0:16:58.70,Default,San,0000,0000,0000,,I still haven't told you that...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:59.45,0:17:01.71,Default,San,0000,0000,0000,,...to your face yet!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:02.59,0:17:04.21,Default,San,0000,0000,0000,,Why is this happening!?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:09.55,0:17:11.88,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Please, God! Give Hotori back to us!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:12.50,0:17:15.09,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't even make it past 16!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:15.09,0:17:18.51,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you do something about it!?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:24.00,0:17:27.02,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time anyone's been this worried about me.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:27.68,0:17:30.23,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to be more careful next time...{I'll throw /a/ a bone here, since they've been spamming that manga page}
Dialogue: 5,0:17:30.23,0:17:31.78,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try to be less of a klutz...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:40.53,0:17:44.83,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah... there won't be a "next time"...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:49.00,0:17:51.34,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Ever... again...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:54.43,0:17:58.09,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to be with them a little longer.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:58.75,0:18:02.64,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to live a little longer!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:07.31,0:18:10.58,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,You must've had a wonderful life if you feel that way.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:10.58,0:18:15.57,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,There are people who end their lives of their own volition, you know. {way to cheer her up, douche.}{inorite}
Dialogue: 5,0:18:15.57,0:18:18.81,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, this place has its good points too.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:18.81,0:18:20.65,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone comes here eventually.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:20.65,0:18:23.33,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,If you just work hard and be patient, you'll see them again soon.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:23.89,0:18:24.58,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:29.23,0:18:30.33,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:30.58,0:18:37.09,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna work hard and make lots of money so I can put bunny ears in their pictures.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:37.09,0:18:38.40,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,That's the spirit!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:38.40,0:18:41.39,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I'll help you find a job then.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:41.60,0:18:47.51,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,You're young, so how about dressing as an angel and greeting the deceased?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:47.51,0:18:49.15,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, like those kids?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:49.15,0:18:51.23,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,My son does it too. {child labor in heaven? wtf japan}
Dialogue: 5,0:18:54.98,0:18:57.03,Default,PA,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Hotori Arashiyama.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:57.48,0:19:01.79,Default,PA,0000,0000,0000,,Please report at once to the Heaven Immigration Bureau.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:01.79,0:19:02.99,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,That's me...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:05.82,0:19:08.37,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,What!? I can go back!?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:08.37,0:19:10.88,Default,Wor,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that seems to be the case.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:10.88,0:19:15.25,Default,Wor,0000,0000,0000,,In your case, your body on Earth is perfectly intact, yes?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:15.46,0:19:21.39,Default,Wor,0000,0000,0000,,Your brain made a miraculous recovery, so you may return if you wish.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:24.17,0:19:27.24,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, you can't come with me, mister.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:27.24,0:19:30.05,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,People return just like you every now and then.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:30.05,0:19:31.90,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,You take care now, and don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:32.09,0:19:35.69,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,When I get back, I'll go visit your grave.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:35.89,0:19:39.65,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but once you return, you'll lose your memory of your time here.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:39.65,0:19:41.28,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's too bad...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:41.28,0:19:43.78,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, hope to see you again next time!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:44.03,0:19:46.79,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,All right, are you ready to go?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:01.48,0:20:04.43,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Being a guide sounds like a nice job and all,
Dialogue: 5,0:20:04.43,0:20:08.31,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,but really, all I do is just help them come to grips with the reality of their deaths.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:08.31,0:20:11.31,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,It's the saddest, most cruel job there is.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:12.22,0:20:17.61,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,That girl being able to return is like a special blessing to me.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:18.35,0:20:21.65,Default,Man2,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's get back to work.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:34.39,0:20:37.84,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like I just had a really weird dream.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:39.59,0:20:43.59,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Huh!? What the heck!? Is this Candid Camera or something!? {that's all google gave me for dokkiri, lol}
Dialogue: 5,0:20:44.22,0:20:48.10,Default,Nurse,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor, come quick! Ms. Arashiyama's awake!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:48.83,0:20:49.96,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The city.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:49.96,0:20:56.42,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,A place where people gather, are born and raised, and one day pass on.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:56.42,0:20:59.05,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But sometimes through the carelessness of the gods,
Dialogue: 5,0:20:59.05,0:21:02.46,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,the lives of the city's residents can be thrown into chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.11,0:21:03.82,Sign,BANANA,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\fs35\fscy140\c&H141B1A&\frz346.034\fnJosschrift Bold\pos(567,602)}Love, Tatsuno
Dialogue: 5,0:21:02.46,0:21:03.82,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, still...
Dialogue: 5,0:21:04.81,0:21:05.95,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,Hotori!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:06.21,0:21:09.20,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kon!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:09.20,0:21:11.45,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,I was worried sick, you idiot! {aww, kon x hotori OTP}{<3}
Dialogue: 5,0:21:11.69,0:21:14.78,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Yet still, the city turns.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:14.78,0:21:20.33,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,So, then once my dad dumped 3,400 yen into the donation box, I woke up.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:20.33,0:21:23.74,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, it's like "you're worth about 3400 yen".
Dialogue: 5,0:21:23.74,0:21:25.65,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds about right.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:25.65,0:21:29.14,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, and about that fountain pendant. {she still can't say it right}
Dialogue: 5,0:21:29.14,0:21:32.92,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,I told them it got crushed when the truck hit me.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:32.92,0:21:35.85,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,Your brain's only good for getting yourself out of trouble, huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:38.99,0:21:40.52,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Hotori.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:40.52,0:21:47.49,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,I think this mess you caught up in was because an evil spirit got a hold of you.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:47.69,0:21:51.55,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Have you gone crazy or something?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:51.55,0:21:53.10,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Why the heck would you say that out of the blue?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:53.10,0:21:55.50,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Just look at this.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:55.72,0:21:56.37,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:56.37,0:21:58.81,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,We took this picture together the other day, remember?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:58.81,0:22:00.21,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,Look at your shoulder.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:00.88,0:22:03.88,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,What's that!? That's freaky!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:06.03,0:22:09.45,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,And the town still turns.
